(256, 1, '2018-03-06 11:27:44', '2018-03-06 11:27:44', '<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n<p class=\"call-inner\">Call <a href=\"callto:(780)757-1900\">(780)757-1900</a> to book an appointment!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Dental Fillings / Restoration in Edmonton</h3>\r\nWhen a tooth has a decay, the dentist should remove the decay and fill the tooth with a biologically and mechanically acceptable material, Amalgam used to be the material of choice in the past, now tooth color materials are available and can provide cosmetically and functionally accepted fillings. This material is called dental composite.\r\nAt Motivo Dental in Edmonton we provide mercury free tooth colored fillings to our patients.\r\nour dentist has provides white fillings that are cosmetically superior to old amalgam fillings, Dr Khaled\r\nAlhomsi has a long experience doing white fillings and dental bonding, we make sure at our dental office you feel comfortable with your new fillings.\r\nAll dental plans are accepted, and we provide low to no interest financing plans to our patients.\r\nPlease don’t hesitate to call us for more information\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 image-design\">\r\n<div class=\"inner-page-outer-img\"><img src=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/about-us-small.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jkwVXM2ZIeQ\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Dental Fillings / Restoration in Edmonton', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'dental-fillings-restoration-in-edmonton-2', '', '', '2018-03-06 12:13:14', '2018-03-06 12:13:14', '', 0, 'http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/?post_type=dental_services&#038;p=256', 0, 'dental_services', '', 0),
