(108, 1, '2018-02-03 09:09:29', '2018-02-03 09:09:29', '<section class=\"inner-page-content\">\r\n <div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n<p class=\"call-inner\">Call<a href=\"callto:(780)757-1900\">(780)757-1900</a> to book an appointment!</p>\r\nDental pain is so unbearable. No one should suffer any longer than they need to. This is why Motivo Dental offers walk-ins and same day appointments for anyone who has a dental emergency.\r\nMotivo Dental offers dental emergency service all days during the week including Saturdays.\r\nDental Emergencies can happen any time of day or night. When it happens, it can be quite stressful. A toothache can come at an instant. Sometimes it hurts with cold water and sometimes cold water actually takes the pain away temporarily. It takes an emergency dentist to properly diagnose your dental problem and determine the best solution. Emergency dentists always perform exam and diagnosis. With assistance from dental x-rays, the proper tooth is treated and things start to get better. Proper antibiotics might be needed in conjunction with the dental treatment in some cases. Contrary to some common belief, an infected tooth should be treated immediately rather than letting it go with antibiotics.\r\n<h3>Our emergency dental team is ready to get you out of dental pain as fast as possible.</h3>\r\n<h3>At Motivo Dental in Edmonton we perform the following emergency dental procedures:</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"about-us-listing\">\r\n 	<li>Dental pain, and Dental and oral infection emergency treatment.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tooth extractions including wisdom teeth</li>\r\n 	<li>Root canal treatments</li>\r\n 	<li>Trauma dentistry</li>\r\n 	<li>Restorative and cosmetic dentistry</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>Motivo Dental provides dental services like <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/emergency/\">emergency dental service</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-implants/\">dental implants</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/braces-orthodontics/\">orthodontics</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/invisalign-invisible-braces/\">invsialign</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-bridges/\">dental bridge</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-crowns/\">dental crowns</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/teeth-whitening/\">teeth whitening</a> etc.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 image-design\"><img src=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/director-img.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jkwVXM2ZIeQ\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', 'EMERGENCY', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-03 09:09:29', '2018-02-03 09:09:29', '', 11, 'http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(110, 1, '2018-02-03 09:29:40', '2018-02-03 09:29:40', '<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n<p class=\"call-inner\">Call<a href=\"callto:(780)757-1900\">(780)757-1900</a> to book an appointment!</p>\r\nProfessional dental cleanings (dental prophylaxis) are usually performed by Registered Dental Hygienists. Your cleaning appointment will include a dental exam and the following:\r\nRemoval of calculus (built ups): Calculus is hardened dental plaque that has been left on the tooth for some time and is now firmly attached to the tooth surface. It can be supra gingival (above the gum) or infra gingival(below the gum). It can’t be removed by home tooth brushing. It can only be removed with special dental instrument used by the professional hygienist or the dentist.\r\nRemoval of dental plaque: Plaque is a sticky, almost invisible film that forms on the teeth. It is a growing colony of living bacteria, food debris, and saliva. The bacteria can start a cavity in the tooth, or/and produce toxins (poisons) that inflame the gums. This gum inflammation is called gingivitis as long as it is confined to the soft tissue. If it spreads to the alveolar bone, it is called periodontitis.\r\n<h3>Fluoride application:</h3>\r\nTopical fluoride is a great preventive way against tooth decay. At Motivo dental we use fluoride for our patients after professional tooth cleaning.\r\n<h3>Teeth polishing:</h3>\r\nRemove stain and plaque that is not otherwise removed during tooth brushing and scaling, it is very important the tooth surface is smooth so it doesn’t retain dental plaque easily.\r\n<h3>Oral hygiene instructions:</h3>\r\nOur professionals will make sure that every patient knows how to brush, floss, and use oral hygiene tools in an efficient way to have good oral health.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 image-design\"><div class=\"inner-page-outer-img\"><img src=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/about-us-small.jpg\" /></div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4hZWLHmtgwU\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/GOppSUwUXlI\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p> </div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Oral Hygiene/ Cleaning', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'oral-hygiene-cleaning__trashed', '', '', '2018-02-06 12:14:28', '2018-02-06 12:14:28', '', 0, 'http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/?page_id=110', 0, 'page', '', 0),
