(124, 1, '2018-02-03 09:55:51', '2018-02-03 09:55:51', '<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n<p class=\"call-inner\">Call <a href=\"callto:(780)757-1900\">(780)757-1900</a> !</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Teeth Whitening</h3>\r\nTeeth whitening at Motivo Dental in Edmonton helps you to have whiter teeth and a beautiful smile\r\n<h3>Teeth Whitening in Edmonton:</h3>\r\nCoffee, tea, smoking and wine – these are just a few of life’s little pleasures that can, over time, stain your teeth and leave you with a less attractive smile. Luckily there are now in office-based and home-based teeth whitening treatments available to undo the damage.\r\nTooth whitening uses a bleaching process to remove stains and discoloration of the teeth and give them a whiter appearance. We offer various methods of teeth whitening in Edmonton, teeth whitening is a great way to stay looking younger! Whitening is one of the most effective and transformative cosmetic dentistry treatments.\r\n<h3>In office teeth whitening</h3>\r\nThe In-office whitening, offering great results in just 60 minutes. Quick and cost effective, the procedure is done at our Edmonton dental office and consists of applying a hydrogen peroxide gel to your teeth, which is then activated for 60 minutes with the whitening light. After the main teeth whitening procedure has taken place, you will receive a set of custom-made trays to maintain your new white smile at home.\r\n<h3>Teeth whitening frequently asked questions</h3>\r\nCould I just use a teeth whitening toothpaste?\r\nFor teeth whitening pastes to really work they would need to be in contact with your teeth for at least 15 minutes, which would never happen during the brushing process. Some teeth whitening toothpastes can even permanently damage your teeth as they contain acids or abrasives.\r\n-What about my fillings or crowns?\r\nBecause fillings or crowns stay the same colour during the teeth whitening process, they may need to be replaced to match the lighter colour of your teeth after completion of the treatment.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 image-design\"><div class=\"inner-page-outer-img\"><img src=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/about-us-small.jpg\" /></div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jkwVXM2ZIeQ\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<div>Motivo Dental provides dental services like <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/emergency/\">emergency dental service</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-implants/\">dental implants</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/braces-orthodontics/\">orthodontics</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/invisalign-invisible-braces/\">invsialign</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-bridges/\">dental bridge</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-crowns/\">dental crowns</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/teeth-whitening/\">teeth whitening</a> etc.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Teeth Whitening', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'teeth-whitening__trashed', '', '', '2018-02-06 12:16:06', '2018-02-06 12:16:06', '', 0, 'http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/?page_id=124', 0, 'page', '', 0);
