ooth.\r\n\r\nImpacted wisdom tooth extractions are indicated for wisdom teeth that have failed to fully erupt. This extraction is also surgical.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'extractions', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'extractions__trashed', '', '', '2018-02-06 12:15:28', '2018-02-06 12:15:28', '', 0, 'http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/?page_id=142', 0, 'page', '', 0),
