n of the tooth and the implant insertion can be done in the same appointment. The patient should be seen by the dentist first to check if immediate dental implants are possible.\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jkwVXM2ZIeQ\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n\n<div>Motivo Dental provides dental services like <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/emergency/\">emergency dental service</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-implants/\">dental implants</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/braces-orthodontics/\">orthodontics</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/invisalign-invisible-braces/\">invsialign</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-bridges/\">dental bridge</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-crowns/\">dental crowns</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/teeth-whitening/\">teeth whitening</a> etc.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n', 'Dental Implants', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '15-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-02-20 09:04:46', '2018-02-20 09:04:46', '', 15, 'http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/15-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
