(228, 1, '2018-02-05 10:16:06', '2018-02-05 10:16:06', '<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n<p class=\"call-inner\">Call <a href=\"callto:(780)757-1900\">(780)757-1900</a> to book an appointment!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Dental Fillings / Restoration in Edmonton</h3>\r\nWhen a tooth has a decay, the dentist should remove the decay and fill the tooth with a biologically and mechanically acceptable material, Amalgam used to be the material of choice in the past, now tooth color materials are available and can provide cosmetically and functionally accepted fillings. This material is called dental composite.\r\nAt Motivo Dental in Edmonton we provide mercury free tooth colored fillings to our patients.\r\nour dentist has provides white fillings that are cosmetically superior to old amalgam fillings, Dr Khaled\r\nAlhomsi has a long experience doing white fillings and dental bonding, we make sure at our dental office you feel comfortable with your new fillings.\r\nAll dental plans are accepted, and we provide low to no interest financing plans to our patients.\r\nPlease don’t hesitate to call us for more information\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 image-design\"><div class=\"inner-page-outer-img\"><img src=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/about-us-small.jpg\" /></div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jkwVXM2ZIeQ\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Dental Fillings / Restoration in Edmonton', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '116-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-05 10:16:06', '2018-02-05 10:16:06', '', 116, 'http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/116-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(229, 1, '2018-02-05 10:16:32', '2018-02-05 10:16:32', '<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n<p class=\"call-inner\">Call <a href=\"callto:(780)757-1900\">(780)757-1900</a> !</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Root Canals</h3>\r\nEach tooth has one root or two or three or maybe four canals. These canals are filled with pulp which is a soft tissue that contains nerves and blood vessels.\r\nWhen the tooth is traumatized, or have a big decay the pulp may become inflamed and infected and need a root canal.\r\nThe tooth that needs a root canal may be sore, but it may also be symptomless.\r\nIn a root canal treatment the canals are accessed, the pulp is removed and each canal space is enlarged and cleaned. The prepared canal space is filled with a special rubber material called gutta percha and a special cement.\r\nThis procedure takes an hour on average.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 image-design\"><div class=\"inner-page-outer-img\"><img src=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/about-us-small.jpg\" /></div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/V1Dv8kbZICo\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<div>Motivo Dental provides dental services like <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/emergency/\">emergency dental service</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-implants/\">dental implants</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/braces-orthodontics/\">orthodontics</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/invisalign-invisible-braces/\">invsialign</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-bridges/\">dental bridge</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-crowns/\">dental crowns</a>, <a href=\"http://webdeve