(237, 1, '2018-02-05 10:24:38', '2018-02-05 10:24:38', '<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n<p class=\"call-inner\">Call <a href=\"callto:(780)757-1900\">(780)757-1900</a> !</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Extractions in Edmonton</h3>\r\n<h3>Good oral hygiene results in a mouth that looks and smells healthy. This means:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"about-us-listing\">\r\n 	<li>Your teeth are clean and free of debris</li>\r\n 	<li>Gums are pink and do not hurt or bleed when you brush or floss</li>\r\n 	<li>Bad breath is not a constant problem</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf your gums do hurt or bleed while brushing or flossing, or you are experiencing persistent bad breath, see your dentist. Any of these conditions may indicate a problem.\r\nYour dentist or hygienist can help you learn good oral hygiene techniques and can help point out areas of your mouth that may require extra attention during brushing and flossing.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 image-design\"><div class=\"inner-page-outer-img\"><img src=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/about-us-small.jpg\" /></div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4hZWLHmtgwU\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/GOppSUwUXlI\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<div>Motivo Dental provides dental services like <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/emergency/\">emergency dental service</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-implants/\">dental implants</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/braces-orthodontics/\">orthodontics</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/invisalign-invisible-braces/\">invsialign</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-bridges/\">dental bridge</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-crowns/\">dental crowns</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/teeth-whitening/\">teeth whitening</a> etc.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<ul class=\"about-us-listing\">\r\n 	<li>If there is a large tooth cavity. If the tooth decay has destroyed a big part of the tooth, extractions may be indicated.</li>\r\n 	<li>If a tooth is causing pain and the patient cannot have a root canal for whatever reason, this may be an indication that a tooth extraction may be necessary.</li>\r\n 	<li>In the case of a tooth already having a root canal that was not crowned or restored properly, therefore having a vertical fracture, an extraction may be needed.</li>\r\n 	<li>Wisdom teeth: If there is no room for wisdom teeth, or if they are not in a favorable position, all or some of those wisdom teeth may need to be extracted. At Motivo Dental in West Edmonton, we perform most types of wisdom teeth extractions.</li>\r\n 	<li>Orthodontic treatments: Sometimes tooth extractions may be recommended to enable the alignment of the other teeth through the course of orthodontic treatment.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTypes of teeth extractions:\r\n\r\nAt Motivo Dental in West Edmonton, we perform simple extractions, surgical extractions, and impacted wisdom tooth extractions.\r\n\r\nSimple extractions are done when the tooth can be pulled out without the need to perform a flap. Usually, these type of extractions are the easiest, but not always possible.\r\n\r\nSurgical extractions are indicated when the tooth is very broken down or anchored to the bone in which case we need a flap, or maybe some bone removal in order to remove the tooth.\r\n\r\nImpacted wisdom tooth extractions are indicated for wisdom teeth that have failed to fully erupt. This extraction is also surgical.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'extractions', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '142-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-05 10:24:38', '2018-02-05 10:24:38', '', 142, 'http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/142-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
