(262, 1, '2018-02-06 10:53:40', '2018-02-06 10:53:40', '<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n<p class=\"call-inner\">Call <a href=\"callto:(780)757-1900\">(780)757-1900</a> to book an appointment!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Dental Fillings / Restoration in Edmonton</h3>\r\nWhen a tooth has a decay, the dentist should remove the decay and fill the tooth with a biologically and mechanically acceptable material, Amalgam used to be the material of choice in the past, now tooth color materials are available and can provide cosmetically and functionally accepted fillings. This material is called dental composite.\r\nAt Motivo Dental in Edmonton we provide mercury free tooth colored fillings to our patients.\r\nour dentist has provides white fillings that are cosmetically superior to old amalgam fillings, Dr Khaled\r\nAlhomsi has a long experience doing white fillings and dental bonding, we make sure at our dental office you feel comfortable with your new fillings.\r\nAll dental plans are accepted, and we provide low to no interest financing plans to our patients.\r\nPlease don’t hesitate to call us for more information\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 image-design\">\r\n<div class=\"inner-page-outer-img\"><img src=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/about-us-small.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jkwVXM2ZIeQ\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Dental Fillings / Restoration in Edmonton', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '116-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-06 10:53:40', '2018-02-06 10:53:40', '', 116, 'http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/116-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(263, 1, '2018-02-06 10:57:14', '2018-02-06 10:57:14', '<div class=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n<p class=\"call-inner\">Call <a href=\"callto:(780)757-1900\">(780)757-1900</a> !</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Dental Crowns in Edmonton</h3>\r\n\r\nYou are a good candidate for dental crowns in these cases:\r\n\r\nIf you have broken or chipped teeth, this damage usually is caused by an injury or from grinding your teeth while sleeping. A dental crown is possibly the most cost effective way to rehabilitate a tooth damaged in these cases.\r\nYou also need a dental crown or cap if you are having a root canal. Usually the tooth loses much of its material when a root canal is done, the tooth also becomes more fragile after root canals. That is why a dental crown is indicated in these cases to cap the tooth and protect it. If a crown is not done after the root canal treatment, the tooth may chip or crack and may be lost because of that.\r\n\r\nDental crowns are also indicated if you have very large fillings. This is to protect the teeth so they don’t chip or crack. Your dentist at Motivo Dental can decide if a crown is good for you.\r\nDental crowns can be made of full porcelain, porcelain fused to metal, or full metal. A discussion with your dentist at Motivo Dental is necessary before deciding the right crown for you.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 image-design\">\r\n<div class=\"inner-page-outer-img\"><img src=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/dental-crown-1.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/JCN3JrxRlOQ\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<div>Motivo Dental provides dental services like <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/emergency/\">emergency dental service</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-implants/\">dental implants</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/braces-orthodontics/\">orthodontics</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/invisalign-invisible-braces/\">invsialign</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-bridges/\">dental bridge</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-crowns/\">dental crowns</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/teeth-whitening/\">teeth whitening</a> etc.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'dental-crowns', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'dental-crowns', '', '', '2018-03-06 11:27:02', '2018-03-06 11:27:02', '', 0, 'http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/?post_type=dental_services&#038;p=263', 0, 'dental_services', '', 0),
(264, 1, '2018-02-06 10:58:27', '2018-02-06 10:58:27', '<div class=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n<p class=\"call-inner\">Dental bridges are used to replace one or more missing teeth. At Motivo Dental we provide dental bridge service for patients who need it.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Indications for Dental Bridges:</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"about-us-listing\">\r\n 	<li>Dental bridges are usually needed when a tooth is lost. The adjacent teeth must be strong enough to hold a fake tooth (a pontic) permanently to replace that missing tooth; in some cases we can replace more than one missing tooth with a long dental bridge.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dental bridges can be used when the teeth adjacent to the missing tooth have large fillings so they can benefit from dental crowns.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dental bridges are also recommended if a dental implant cannot be done to replace the missing tooth.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Materials Used for Dental Bridges</h3>\r\n<strong>At Motivo Dental in west Edmonton we make all types of dental bridges.</strong>\r\n<p>This includes: </p>\r\n<ul class=\"about-us-listing\">\r\n<li>All ceramic bridges </li>\r\n<li>Porcelain fused to metal bridges </li>\r\n<li>Metal bridges. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Please call Motivo Dental to learn more about the options.</p>\r\n<h3>Procedure:</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"about-us-listing\">\r\n<li>In order to make a dental bridge, the adjacent teeth should be prepared to receive crowns. The fake tooth that will replace the missing tooth will be held by these crowns.</li>\r\n<li>The first step is to take the records, which may include pictures, x-rays, or study models. After studying these records, the treatment plan is prepared, and the color/shade is chosen.</li>\r\n<li>The second step is to prepare the adjacent teeth for the crowns. Impressions need to be taken, and a temporary bridge needs to be cemented on. The impression is sent to a dental lab to manufacture the bridge.</li>\r\n<li>The next appointment you get the bridge cemented on. The dentist checks the bite, the function, and the esthetics.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Alternative Options for Replacing Teeth</h3>\r\n<p>At Motivo Dental in west Edmonton we can also replace missing teeth by using Dental Implants, or removable partial dentures. A consultation with the dentist is necessary to decide which treatment option is best for you.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 image-design\">\r\n<div class=\"inner-page-outer-img\"><img src=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bridges-1.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/GOppSUwUXlI\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<div>Motivo Dental provides dental services like <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/emergency/\">emergency dental service</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-implants/\">dental implants</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/braces-orthodontics/\">orthodontics</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/invisalign-invisible-braces/\">invsialign</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-bridges/\">dental bridge</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-crowns/\">dental crowns</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/teeth-whitening/\">teeth whitening</a> etc.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'dental bridges', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'dental-bridges', '', '', '2018-03-06 11:25:08', '2018-03-06 11:25:08', '', 0, 'http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/?post_type=dental_services&#038;p=264', 0, 'dental_services', '', 0),
(265, 1, '2018-02-06 10:59:17', '2018-02-06 10:59:17', '<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\r\n<p class=\"call-inner\">Call <a href=\"callto:(780)757-1900\">(780)757-1900</a> !</p>\r\nAt Motivo Dental in Edmonton west we try to preserve teeth as much as we can, unfortunately sometimes the teeth can be hopeless and need to come out, in these cases we perform dental extractions.\r\n<strong>Some indications for teeth extractions:</strong>\r\n<ul class=\"about-us-listing\">\r\n 	<li>A very big tooth cavity, if the tooth decay has destroyed a very big part of the tooth extractions may be indicated.</li>\r\n 	<li>A tooth that has toothache and the patient can not have a root canal for some reason, in this case a tooth extraction may be indicated.</li>\r\n 	<li>A tooth that already had a root canal, and for some reason was not crowned or restored properly, and has a vertical fracture ; in this case an extraction may be needed .</li>\r\n 	<li>Wisdom teeth: if there is no room for wisdom teeth, or if they are not in a favorable position, all or some of those wisdom teeth may need to be extracted. At Motivo Dental in West Edmonton, we perform most types of wisdom teeth extractions.</li>\r\n 	<li>Orthodontic treatments: Sometimes teeth extractions maybe indicated to enable the alignment of the other teeth in the course of orthodontic treatment.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Types of teeth extractions:</strong>\r\n<ul class=\"about-us-listing\">\r\n 	<li>At Motivo Dental in west Edmonton we perform simple extractions, surgical extractions, and impacted wisdom teeth extractions.</li>\r\n 	<li>Simple extractions are done when the tooth can be pulled out without the need to perform a flap,usually this type of extractions is the easiest but not always possible.</li>\r\n 	<li>Surgical extractions are indicated when the tooth is so much broken down, or very anchored to the bone that we need a flap or maybe some bone removal to be able to remove the tooth.</li>\r\n 	<li>Impacted wisdom teeth extractions are indicated for wisdom teeth that failed to fully erupt, this extraction is surgical .</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 image-design\">\r\n<div class=\"inner-page-outer-img\"><img src=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/extraction-1.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4hZWLHmtgwU\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<p class=\"about-us-iframe\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/GOppSUwUXlI\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row row-bg-design\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n<div>Motivo Dental provides dental services like <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/emergency/\">emergency dental service</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-implants/\">dental implants</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/braces-orthodontics/\">orthodontics</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/invisalign-invisible-braces/\">invsialign</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-bridges/\">dental bridge</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/dental-crowns/\">dental crowns</a>, <a href=\"http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/services/teeth-whitening/\">teeth whitening</a> etc.</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'extractions', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'extractions', '', '', '2018-03-06 11:21:25', '2018-03-06 11:21:25', '', 0, 'http://webdevelopers1.com/motivodental/?post_type=dental_services&#038;p=265', 0, 'dental_services', '', 0);
